item.title: BWF World Rankings: Two-time Olympic medallist P.V Sindhu breaks into top five, Prannoy moves to 12th
item.description: BWF World Rankings: Two-time Olympic medallist P.V Sindhu breaks into top five, Prannoy moves to 12th Commonwealth Games gold medallist Sindhu, who has 87,218 points from 26 tournaments, displaced arch-rival Carolina Marin of Spain in the fifth position
